Enum Class TokenType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<TokenType>
TokenType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<TokenType>, Constable
public enum TokenType extends Enum<TokenType>
TokenType is an enum class that contains all the token types, use as the ret value of the scanner.

1.0 (Last Update 2023/06/01)
